179
00:23:39,084 --> 00:23:43,817
I burst crackers for him,
but he drops a bomb on me

180
00:23:44,089 --> 00:23:46,114
He is praising her too much.
- I will praise her!

181
00:23:46,825 --> 00:23:50,591
Son-in-law, the bullock cart journey
must've been tiring

182
00:23:50,829 --> 00:23:52,194
Go take a shower and rest

183
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:58,128
What, what is this?
- Brother, let us not have him here

184
00:23:58,336 --> 00:24:00,600
For what?
- We don't need him here

185
00:24:00,839 --> 00:24:04,297
If you allow him to enter, we may
lose many valuables. Be careful

186
00:24:04,509 --> 00:24:07,307
Don't blabber.
- Am I blabbering?

187
00:24:10,949 --> 00:24:13,816
He is calling me over...
did he hear what I just said?

188
00:24:17,255 --> 00:24:19,985
