He ditched me! Oh God!

233
00:27:10,195 --> 00:27:12,993
He left me alone.
How will I go out?

234
00:27:13,198 --> 00:27:19,899
I've to go 1 k.m. From here.
Gopal, take me along. Where are you?

235
00:27:28,213 --> 00:27:32,843
He came with me,
and ditched me, murderer

236
00:27:40,392 --> 00:27:42,121
A lion!

237
00:28:34,112 --> 00:28:37,570
Brother Murugesh, look at me

238
00:28:37,782 --> 00:28:42,082
Say something... please

239
00:28:42,787 --> 00:28:46,245
Didn't I ask you not to take him there?
Just look at him

240
00:28:46,458 --> 00:28:50,417
He looks like one of those big shots,
frozen with a smile while being arrested

241
00:28:50,628 --> 00:28:51,993
What to do now?

242
00:29:06,644 --> 00:29:11,547
Sister...? Why is there a crowd here?
What happened?

243
00:29:11,816 --> 00:29:14,216
Greetings, I am...
- not the groom

244
00:29:15,320 --> 00:29:17,447
Where is my prospective son-in-law?

245
00:29:18,490 --> 00:29:21,618
When they said, you came by bullock cart...

246
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:24,788
I knew that you were not my son in law

247
00:29:25,330 --> 00:29:29,960
Because his son wouldn't come like that.
- You said it right

248
00:29:30,168 --> 00:29:35,629
I tried to tell them
I am not the groom...

249
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:37,239
but they don't believe me

250
00:29:37,509 --> 00:29:39,704
But you've understood it on your own

251
00:29:41,346 --> 00:29:45,043
The groom has decided to buy
'Vettayapuram Palace' in this village

252
00:29:46,518 --> 00:29:50,318
He has sent me for that. I am his friend.
I've been brought up in his house

253
00:29:50,522 --> 00:29:52,319
My name is Saravanan.
- Impossible!

254
00:29:52,524 --> 00:29:56,483
I won't allow him to buy
the 'Vettayapuram Palace'

255
00:29:56,694 --> 00:30:00,824
lt'll be dangerous for him to buy that

256
00:30:01,199 --> 00:30:02,826
For my daughter too,
who will marry him

257
00:30:03,034 --> 00:30:04,934
Well, lady...

258
00:30:05,870 --> 00:30:07,167
I don't know how to say this.

259
00:30:07,705 --> 00:30:09,332
His marrying your daughter...

260
00:30:09,541 --> 00:30:10,838
There he comes

261
00:30:11,876 --> 00:30:13,844
He resembles his dad

262
00:30:18,216 --> 00:30:19,683
You? Son in law?

263
00:30:24,556 --> 00:30:28,515
Priya, come here.
You wanted to see your fiance

264
00:30:28,726 --> 00:30:31,752
He has arrived. Come and see him

265
00:30:37,235 --> 00:30:38,532
Who's that?

266
00:30:39,070 --> 00:30:40,765
She is Ganga

267
00:30:42,073 --> 00:30:43,040
My wife

268
00:30:46,244 --> 00:30:50,374
His mother wanted him
to marry your adopted daughter...

269
00:30:50,582 --> 00:30:54,712
but due to certain circumstances,
Senthil had to marry Ganga

270
00:30:55,086 --> 00:30:58,886
What is this? People from big families
asked for my daughter's hand...

271
00:30:59,090 --> 00:31:01,388
but I didn't agree,
but you have deserted us

272
00:31:01,593 --> 00:31:05,120
Marriages and alliances are decided
by destiny. How can we control it?

273
00:31:05,430 --> 00:31:09,230
What a knowledge at such an young age?

274
00:31:09,601 --> 00:31:12,570
You have Avvaiyar's brain. Shake hand

275
00:31:12,770 --> 00:31:14,067
Let it be

276
00:31:14,272 --> 00:31:17,241
My marriage definitely would have
hurt you

277
00:31:17,442 --> 00:31:22,243
But I've come here only to see you all.
Pardon me

278
00:31:22,947 --> 00:31:24,744
We shall leave now.
- Where?

279
00:31:24,949 --> 00:31:29,249
I've bought 'Vettayapuram Palace'.
We shall be staying there

280
00:31:29,621 --> 00:31:31,418
You mean THAT palace? Please don't

281
00:31:31,623 --> 00:31:34,251
Why?
- I went to see it, and I got a shock

282
00:31:34,459 --> 00:31:36,256
If you buy it,
you'd be inviting trouble

283
00:31:36,461 --> 00:31:38,759
Uncle, you are all elderly,
this is what you believe

284
00:31:38,963 --> 00:31:44,265
Listen to me. Just like my uncle,
you also married an outside girl

285
00:31:44,469 --> 00:31:47,597
However, I won't allow you to stay
in such a dangerous place

286
00:31:47,805 --> 00:31:51,764
Uncle, before coming here
Ganga and I visited that palace

287
00:31:51,976 --> 00:31:54,274
Nothing is scary over there like he said

288
00:31:54,479 --> 00:32:00,111
Don't mistake me, I've been a gardener
in that palace for 40 years

289
00:32:00,318 --> 00:32:04,448
Even I've not gone inside that palace.
Please think and act

290
00:32:04,656 --> 00:32:10,788
I've bought that 50-crore worth
property for 5 crore rupees...

291
00:32:10,995 --> 00:32:11,962
I know that people believe that
it has some problems

292
00:32:12,830 --> 00:32:18,462
But I don't believe it. I want my wife
Ganga to be the owner...

293
00:32:18,670 --> 00:32:21,468
of a palace instead of just a house.
That's why I bought it

294
00:32:21,673 --> 00:32:24,801
In case of any problems, we'll deal
with it. You don't worry

295
00:32:25,009 --> 00:32:26,135
Go stay there

296
00:32:31,015 --> 00:32:33,074
You may go and stay in that house

297
00:32:35,853 --> 00:32:40,756
Why do you stare? I stood against buying
that house. Are you wondering...

298
00:32:41,526 --> 00:32:43,653
