317
00:34:29,801 --> 00:34:34,204
Specifically no one should go to
the room in the southern corner

318
00:34:35,807 --> 00:34:39,607
You have decided to stay with us with
your family. Won't I do atleast this?

319
00:34:39,811 --> 00:34:42,780
We shall stay away from
that place for sure

320
00:34:43,981 --> 00:34:45,676
Now I am happy

321
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:51,550
Oh God! What would I do?

322
00:34:51,823 --> 00:34:55,122
Why do they buy trouble
and decorate it nicely?

323
00:34:55,993 --> 00:34:59,793
I shouldn't stay alone in the house.
I should always be with the others

324
00:34:59,997 --> 00:35:01,021
Murugesa!

325
00:35:02,500 --> 00:35:06,561
Such a beautiful name. Why do you
call it in such a scary manner?

326
00:35:08,172 --> 00:35:10,037
Why do you create trouble?
- I have a sore throat

327
00:35:10,508 --> 00:35:13,568
I forgot to ask, what is
your zodiac sign?

328
00:35:14,178 --> 00:35:16,146
Why?
Just tell me

329
00:35:16,848 --> 00:35:20,909
Leo.
- Leo, really?

330
00:35:21,519 --> 00:35:24,147
Only one in a lakh will
have this zodiac sign

331
00:35:25,356 --> 00:35:27,324
You are lucky

332
00:35:29,193 --> 00:35:31,388
Ghosts love that sign!

333
